# ✨ feat(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# <footer>

# Type prefix with emoji:
# ✨ feat:     New feature
# 🐛 fix:      Bug fix
# 📚 docs:     Documentation only changes
# 🎨 style:    Changes that do not affect the meaning of the code
# ♻️  refactor: A code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
# 🧪 test:     Adding missing tests or correcting existing tests
# 🔧 chore:    Changes to the build process or auxiliary tools
# ⚡ perf:     A code change that improves performance
# 👷 ci:       Changes to CI configuration files and scripts
# 📦 build:    Changes that affect the build system or external dependencies
# ⏪ revert:   Reverts a previous commit

# Scope (optional): service, tool, config, test, etc.

# Subject: imperative mood, no period, max 50 chars
# Body: explain what and why (optional)
# Footer: breaking changes, issue references (optional)

# Examples:
# ✨ feat(service): add gemini image generation support
# 🐛 fix(tool): handle api rate limiting errors
# 📚 docs: update installation instructions
# 🧪 test(service): add unit tests for style catalog